PROJECT.NAME: jaClaCaes1-mito
PROJECT.TITLE: Cladocora caespitosa, mitochondrial assembly, jaClaCaes1-mito.
PROJECT.DESCRIPTION: This project collects the mitochondrial assembly of Cladocora caespitosa. The assembly is provided by the European Reference Genome Atlas (ERGA, https://www.erga-biodiversity.eu/) via the Biodiversity Genomics Europe project (BGE, https://biodiversitygenomics.eu/).
